268
00:17:27,728 --> 00:17:30,528
tapi kurasa dia mempercayai adiknya?

269
00:17:30,528 --> 00:17:32,528
Tidak, kurasa bukan begitu.

270
00:17:32,528 --> 00:17:34,628
