273
00:17:39,128 --> 00:17:40,828
Lalu, kau berinisiatif

274
00:17:40,828 --> 00:17:43,128
dan menikam direktur di hadapannya.

275
00:17:44,828 --> 00:17:47,128
Lalu, setelah Moyono mulai mempercayaimu

276
00:17:47,128 --> 00:17:50,228
